data-triple-N3.o: "Nickelodeon (often simply called Nick and originally called The Pinwheel Network) is an American basic cable and satellite television network that is operated by the MTV Networks Kids & Family Group unit of Viacom. Aimed mainly at pre-teens and teenagers 11–16 years of age and its preschooler-targeted shows aimed at children 2–6, it broadcasts on Sundays from 6 a.m. - 8 p.m. , Monday-Thursdays from 7 a.m.-8 p.m. , Fridays from 7 a.m.-9 p.m. and Saturdays from 6 a.m.-10 p.m.."@en
